# Status:  Modula-3 + cm3 — 161+ stars on modula3/cm3, active
#          maintenance since community takeover; PM3 (alternative)
#          on Modula-3/pm3.  Modula-3 has a SMALL but DEDICATED
#          community of language enthusiasts + ex-DEC SRC
#          alumni continuing the tradition.  Used in: SRC's
